profile:
Orsi Szekely Interior Design, Decorating, Home Staging welcomes you to our company profile. My name is Orsi and I am an Interior Decorator. This is my portfolio where I feature interior design, decorating projects,and home staging. I am a true lover of color and well organized spaces and I aim to help my clients and friends increase the value of their home and achieve their personal taste and harmony in the space they live or work.

I have demonstrated success in transforming ideas into beautiful and functional design solutions for client spaces. Accomplished in creative planning from concept development to research, layout and design.
licenses: Accredited Member of the Canadian Decorators & Designers Association of Canada

profile:
Tina Nikoukar has been painting “still life” & “Walt Disney’s cartoon characters” since she was 6 years old as she always cared about nature and animals having the same values as humans. In her teenage years, she started to paint Persian miniature characters.
The name 5 Cats Art Gallery is derived from her five family cats. She has been painting “still life” since she was 14 years old, and painting abstract on canvas professionally for almost ten years.
The main type of mediums that she uses are both oil and acrylic paints. However, she prefers other mediums such as charcoals, pastels, pencils, and water colors to teach in her art classes.
name: 5 Cats Art Gallery
